上一代型号的 4.7 倍。也就是说，它也比 Pocket 2 发布时贵得多。它在美国的售价为 520 美元，比 Pocket 2 贵 170 美元。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/djis-osmo-pocket-3-features-a-1-inch-sensor-and-rotating-display-130055176.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-tv-prices-have-doubled-in-just-over-a-year-150156333.html">Apple TV+ 价格在短短一年多时间里翻了一番</a></h2><h3>Apple One、Arcade 和 News+ 套餐现在也更加昂贵。</h3><h3></h3><p> Apple TV+ 的价格每月上涨 3 美元，达到 10 美元。年度 TV+ 套餐已从 69 美元涨至 99 美元。 Apple Arcade 现在每月 7 美元，而不是 5 美元。至于 Apple News+，独立订阅的费用现在为每月 10 美元，现在为 13 美元。 Apple TV+ 订阅费用此前从每月 5 美元上涨到 2022 年 10 月的 7 美元，这意味着该服务的价格在短短 12 个月内翻了一番。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-tv-prices-have-doubled-in-just-over-a-year-150156333.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p><p></p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktoks-first-live-global-music-event-will-feature-cardi-b-and-charlie-puth-141212595.html">TikTok 首个现场“全球音乐盛会”将由 Cardi B 和 Charlie Puth 主演</a></h2><h3>In The Mix 将于 12 月 10 日在亚利桑那州举行。</h3> <a href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktoks-first-live-global-music-event-will-feature-cardi-b-and-charlie-puth-141212595.html"><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/2524bd10-73df-11ee-aaa6-de2dbcce8e5b" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/2524bd10-73df-11ee-aaa6-de2dbcce8e5b" style="height:347px;width:675px;" alt="TMA" data-uuid="2087e11b-a8eb-3760-a399-a5b152678cc6"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">抖音</div></figure></a><p>TikTok In The Mix 将于 12 月 10 日在亚利桑那州梅萨举行，这是该视频平台的首个全球现场音乐活动。头条新闻包括 Cardi B、Niall Horan、Anitta 和 Charlie Puth，还有令人惊喜的嘉宾和新兴艺术家的表演。从 10 月 27 日开始，四位头条人物的追随者将获得预售代码来购买 In The Mix 门票。一般销售将于 11 月 2 日开始，TikTok 也将在其应用程序上直播该活动。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktoks-first-live-global-music-event-will-feature-cardi-b-and-charlie-puth-141212595.html"><strong>继续阅读。</strong></a></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-metas-threads-reaches-almost-100-million-active-users-111509107.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-morning-after-metas-threads-reaches-almost-100-million-active-users-111509107.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e4530cf4-92e2-4516-aac1-4a704f7290d7</guid><dc:creator>马特·史密斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 26 Oct 2023 11:15:09 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1698312188</ingested><modified> 2023-10-26T09:23:14+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Small Businesses]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mat Smith]]></category><media:content height="3841" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/27ba3cf0-71da-11ee-b27b-526409a863c9" width="6428"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3841" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/27ba3cf0-71da-11ee-b27b-526409a863c9" width="6428"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NurPhoto via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Meta logo is seen on a phone with the Instagram Threads app logo in the background in this illustration photo on 06 Ju